'''硫代甲醛'''（{{lang-en|Thioformaldehyde}}）是一種[[有機硫化合物|有機硫化合物]]，化學式為{{chem|CH|2|S}}。

== 簡介 ==
硫代甲醛的結構式首次由義大利化學家西爾維奧·貝茲（Silvio Bezzi）確認。<ref>{{cite journal|first=Ugo|last=Croatto|title=BEZZI, Silvio|journal=Dizionario Biografico degli Italiani|volume=9|year=1967|editor=Treccani|access-date=2017-09-16|url=http://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/silvio-bezzi_(Dizionario-Biografico)/|archive-date=2017-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918064826/http://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/silvio-bezzi_(Dizionario-Biografico)/|dead-url=no}}</ref>一個人工製備的方法是在10 K溫度的氬基質中對三硫代碳酸甲酯{{chem|C|2|H|2|S|3}}進行[[光分解作用|光分解作用]]。<ref>{{cite journal|first=M.|last=Torres |first2=I. |last2=Safarik |first3=A. |last3= Clement|first4=O. P. |last4=Strausz|journal=Canadian Journal of Chemistry|year= 1982|volume= 60|issue=10|pp=1187-1191|doi=10.1139/v82-176|url=http://www.nrcresearchpress.com/doi/pdf/10.1139/v82-176|format=pdf|access-date=2017-09-17|title=The generation and vibrational spectrum of matrix isolated thioformaldehyde and dideuterothioformaldehyde }}</ref>

此化合物在日常環境中並不穩定，極易形成其[[低聚物|低聚物]]，即具有相同[[實驗式|實驗式]]的[[1,3,5-三硫雜環己烷|1,3,5-三硫雜環己烷]]，因此十分罕見。然而在星際物質中則能觀察到其存在，<ref>Despois, D., "Radio Line Observations of Molecular and Isotopic Species in Comet C/1995 O1 (Hale-Bopp) Implications on the Interstellar Origin of Cometary Ices", Earth, Moon, Planets 1999, 79, 103-124.</ref>鼓勵了對其性質的研究。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1146/annurev.pc.34.100183.000335|title=The Spectroscopy of Formaldehyde and Thioformaldehyde|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_annual-review-of-physical-chemistry_1983_34/page/31|year=1983|last1=Clouthier|first1=D. J.|last2=Ramsay|first2=D. A.|journal=Annual Review of Physical Chemistry|volume=34|pages=31–58|bibcode=1983ARPC...34...31C}}</ref>藉[[紅外光譜學|紅外光譜儀]]可得知其存在於緻密高速雲CO-0.40-0.22等[[星際雲|星際雲]]，<ref name="oka">{{cite journal|first=Tomoharu|last=Oka|3=|first2=Reiko|last2=Mizuno|first3=Kodai|last3=Miura|first4=Shunya|last4=Takekawa|title=Signature of an Intermediate-Mass Black Hole in the Central Zone of our Galaxy|journal=The Astrophysical Journal Letters|date=2015-12-28|volume=816|issue=1|page=L7|doi=10.3847/2041-8205/816/1/L7|access-date=2017-09-14|editor=The American Astronomical Society|url=http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.3847/2041-8205/816/1/L7/meta;jsessionid=C74139C78BBC3247565E130457D2E5FF.c4.iopscience.cld.iop.org|arxiv=1512.04661|bibcode=2016ApJ...816L...7O|archive-date=2017-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912023038/http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.3847/2041-8205/816/1/L7/meta|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及[[海爾-博普彗星|海爾-博普彗星]]之[[彗髮|彗髮]]。<ref>{{cite journal|first=L. M.|last=Woodney|first2=M. F.|last2=A'Hearn|first3=J.|last3=McMullin|first4=N.|last4=Samarasinha|title=Sulfur Chemistry at Millimeter Wavelengths in C/Hale-Bopp|journal=Earth, Moon, and Planets|volume=78|issue=1-3|pp=69—70|date=1997-07|access-date=2017-09-16|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1023%2FA%3A1006275412491|archive-date=2017-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918064756/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1023%2FA:1006275412491|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|first=D.|last=Despois|title=radio Line Observations of Molecular and Isotopic Species in Comet C/1995 O1 (Hale-Bopp) Implications on the Interstellar Origin of Cometary Ices|journal=Earth, Moon, and Planets|volume=79|issue=1-3|pages=103-124|date=1997-09|access-date=2017-09-16|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1023/A:1006229131864|archive-date=2017-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918064301/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1023/A:1006229131864|dead-url=no}}</ref>

由於雙鍵原理，硫代甲醛傾向形成鏈狀或環狀結構。已知其存在於數種[[配位化合物|配位化合物]]中，包括以下的{{chem|Os(SCH|2|)(CO)|2|(PPh|3|)|2}}。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1039/C0DT00975J|title=The coordination chemistry of small sulfur-containing molecules: A personal perspective|year=2011|last1=Schenk|first1=Wolfdieter A.|journal=Dalton Trans|volume=40|issue=6|pages=1209–1219|pmid=21088787}}</ref>
